'''Khorasani Arabic''' is a [[varieties of Arabic|dialect]] of Arabic spoken in Iran.  It is a variety of [[Central Asian Arabic]] spoken in the [[Iran]]ian province of [[Khorasan Province|Khorasan]].<ref>Ulrich Seeger, ''[https://www.academia.edu/10319772/On_the_Relationship_of_the_Central_Asian_Arabic_Dialects On the Relationship of the Central Asian Arabic Dialects]'' (translated from German to English by Sarah Dickins)</ref> Khorasani Arabic is not taught in school and is not spoken by the majority of Khorosani Arabs.

